This is an overview of the project.
It consists of the following:
- an arduino uno
- a python script polling an api provider

1) arduino setup
The setup consists of a 1602 LCD screen, an arduino uno, a buzzer, and a breadboard. When the arduino receives data from the serial port, it displays the data on the LCD and buzzes.

2) python script
Polls api for data and sends that data via a serial port.

